OL,3,CDevon MPs call for u-turn on axing of
OL,4,C#50 South West Water bill subsidy
OL,6,FRebecca Smith, who has represented
OL,7,FSouth West Devon since the general
OL,8,Felection in July, is one of the MPs
OL,9,Fwho has written to the Environment
OL,10,FSecretary asking him to u-turn on the
OL,11,Fdecision.
OL,13,FShe wrote: "We wish to reiterate the
OL,14,Fneed for the #50 water bill rebate to
OL,15,Fbe reinstated. We're not asking for
OL,16,Fany special favours, just that the
OL,17,Fcost to keep Britain's prized beaches
OL,18,Fclean is fairly distributed."
