OL,3,CDevon MPs call for u-turn on axing of
OL,4,C#50 South West Water bill subsidy
OL,6,FSouth West Water says the government's
OL,7,Fannual subsidy was "important" in
OL,8,Fensuring bills were "manageable" for
OL,9,Fconsumers in a region where 3% of the
OL,10,FUK population helps look after a third
OL,11,Fof the country's coastline.
OL,13,FMs Smith and other Tories from Devon
OL,14,Fare warning that the refusal to extend
OL,15,Fthe subsidy, alongside a rise in
OL,16,Fhousehold bills from next year, will
OL,17,Ffurther squeeze household budgets and
OL,18,F"widen the gulf between the South West
OL,19,Fand the rest of the UK where annual
OL,20,Fsalaries sit #921 below the national
OL,21,Faverage."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
