OL,3,CDevon MPs call for u-turn on axing of
OL,4,C#50 South West Water bill subsidy
OL,6,F"This feeds into the broader picture
OL,7,Fof a Budget which did not mention the
OL,8,FSouth West once," she adds.
OL,10,FLabour maintains it is "fixing the
OL,11,Ffoundations to put public finances on
OL,12,Fa sustainable path to restore
OL,13,Fstability" and has had to make
OL,14,F"difficult decisions on tax, welfare
OL,15,Fand spending" since taking office on
OL,16,FJuly.
