OL,3,CDevon MPs call for u-turn on axing of
OL,4,C#50 South West Water bill subsidy
OL,6,FOn not continuing the annual rebate
OL,7,Ffor water customers in the South West,
OL,8,Fthe government explained: "The rebate
OL,9,Fwas originally introduced in 2013
OL,10,Fbecause SWW customers faced
OL,11,Fsignificantly higher water bills than
OL,12,Fcustomers in other regions due to the
OL,13,Flevel of investment the company was
OL,14,Frequired to make in the region's
OL,15,Finfrastructure to meet environmental
OL,16,Fand water quality standards.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
