OL,3,CDevon MPs call for u-turn on axing of
OL,4,C#50 South West Water bill subsidy
OL,6,F"Over the last decade, the difference
OL,7,Fbetween water bills in the south-west
OL,8,Fregion and others has decreased. Over
OL,9,Fthe next price review period, 2025 to
OL,10,F2029, Ofwat's latest projections are
OL,11,Fthat SWW customers' bills will be
OL,12,Fsimilar to those in other regions."
OL,14,FIt added: "The Government are
OL,15,Fcommitted to taking action to address
OL,16,Fwater poverty and help vulnerable
OL,17,Fcustomers with their water bills.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
