OL,3,CDevon MPs call for u-turn on axing of
OL,4,C#50 South West Water bill subsidy
OL,6,F"All water companies have measures in
OL,7,Fplace for people who struggle to pay
OL,8,Ffor their water and waste water
OL,9,Fservices, including measures such as
OL,10,FWaterSure, social tariffs, payment
OL,11,Fbreaks and holidays, and debt
OL,12,Fmanagement support.
OL,14,F"We expect all water companies to
OL,15,Fproactively engage with their
OL,16,Fcustomers to ensure that they know
OL,17,Fwhat support schemes are available and
OL,18,Fhow to use them."
